               <p>JOANNAH LEONARD. I am <rs id="t18261207-151-viclabel894" type="occupation">single</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-151-victim897 t18261207-151-viclabel894"></join> - the prisoner lodged four days with me. On the 13th of November, the watchman awoke me - I found the prisoner at the watch-<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182612070069"></xptr>house with this property, which he had taken from the back room.</p>
